{"id":"api/core/if","title":"@if","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/if\", \"name\": \"@if\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/if.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"if\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e9c0d38mtidy1sxzi709q43po\">@if<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/if#if\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label block\">block</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c90qhk9p9wjt5558zezldzym0\"><code><a href=\"api/core/if\" class=\"code-anchor\">@if</a></code> 區塊在條件表示式為真時有條件地顯示其內容。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/if#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n    <h2 id=\"syntax\">語法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/if#syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <code-example language=\"html\">\n@if (a &gt; b) {\n  {{a}} is greater than {{b}}\n} @else if (b &gt; a) {\n  {{a}} is less than {{b}}\n} @else {\n  {{a}} is equal to {{b}}\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/if#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"55ft759nj8fqni9ogu4hpitx3\">根據 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/if\" class=\"code-anchor\">@if</a></code> 和 \n<code>@else</code> 塊中條件表示式的評估，內容會被新增到 DOM 中或從中移除。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ez9usueo98gxcuf32ltu1eqe4\">內建的 \n<code><a href=\"api/core/if\" class=\"code-anchor\">@if</a></code> 支援引用表示式結果，以保持常見編碼模式的解決方案：</p>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n@if (users$ | <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>; as users) {\n  {{ users.length }}\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/control_flow\n - guide/signal-queries\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/if#description\n - api/core/if#if\n - api/core/if#syntax\n - api/platform-browser/animations/async\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/if.md\n-->"}